 <p>
  <b>Rule-6 ᐅ </b>
  Active sentence যার নিম্নরূপ কাঠামো ᐅ
  Subject + verb + object +present participle-একে নিম্নরূপে passive করা হয় ᐅ 
 </p>
 <card>Object-এর subject+ Tense এবং person-অনুসারে Auxiliary verb + Verb-এর past participle+ present participle-যুক্ত অংশ+ by + subject-এর object।</card>
 <h3>Example ᐅ </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>I saw him performing the dance. (Active)</li>
  <li>He was seen performing the dance by me. (Passive)</li>
 </ul>
